  "title": "HR Manager (Manufacturing/MNC/Tampines)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Job Title: </strong>HR Manager</p></li><li><p><strong>Type:</strong> German MNC</p></li><li><p><strong>Industry: </strong>Semiconductor / Electronics</p></li><li><p><strong>Location: </strong>Tampines</p></li></ul><p><strong>Main Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Ensure pay remains competitive through industry benchmarking, manage annual merit increments, and oversee bonus planning. Responsible for legal compliance (MOM/RBA) and leading the annual budgeting process.</p></li><li><p>Guide the HR Administrator to identify skill gaps, source training programs, and facilitate career development initiatives aligned with business goals.</p></li><li><p>Act as a bridge between local operations and HQ, while driving continuous improvement and specialized HR projects.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Degree</strong> in <strong>HR Management</strong> (or a related field).</p></li><li><p><strong>3 years</strong> in a managerial role, specifically within a <strong>24/7 manufacturing</strong> setting. Deep expertise in <strong>payroll</strong> is mandatory.</p></li><li><p>Strong grasp of <strong>Singapore employment laws</strong>, meticulous attention to detail, and the ability to engage effectively with teams.</p></li></ul><p>For interested applicants, kindly send your resume in Word/PDF format to include the following in your resume including:</p><p>1. Current Salary</p><p>2. Expected Salary</p><p>3. Availability</p><p>4. Reason for leaving</p><p>Thank you for your application and we regret that only shortlisted applicants will be notified</p><p>By submitting any application or resume to us, you will be deemed to have agreed & consented to us collecting, using, retaining & disclosing your personal information to prospective employers with the services provided by us.</p><p>Nguyen Thi Doan | R23116355</p><p>RRecruiter Pte. Ltd. | 18C9514</p>",
