    "description": "<p>RRecruiter is an international recruitment agency specialized in headhunting for executives, managers and experts. We serve as a strategic partner to our clients, offering a turnkey solution to capture and deliver the top talent needed to complete successful projects by aligning with the unique needs of our clients. Our timely action plan significantly saves client’s time and costs.</p>\n<p>Our passion is to deliver outstanding customer service to the companies and candidates that we partner. Developing long term and mutually beneficial relationships is the key to our success.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Recruitment Experts in Singapore, Thailand, Vietnam, Philippines &amp; Indonesia market</li>\n  <li>Dedicated Key Account Personnel to handle client relationship</li>\n  <li>Unique database of candidates</li>\n  <li>Access to leading job boards and CV database</li>\n  <li>Extensive experience in sourcing and selecting for key position</li>\n</ul>\n<p>More information: https://rrecruiterint.com/</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>https://rrecruiter-pte-ltd.breezy.hr/</p>",
